{"Id":546008,"Title":"家训","Dynasty":"明","Author":"邹元标","Context":"诗咏多福，易言馀庆。积善之家，罔不繁盛。眇予小子，厕名士绅。愧无实德，裨补君民。未能治国，愿教吾家。敷诚布衷，寂听无哗。凡我宗人，无忽予言。洗心涤虑，培根达源。敬奉天地，孝养双亲。与其浊富，宁守清贫。勿利货贿，嘱托上官。小民叫冤，尔心何安。输赋无讼，迹绝公室。尊宪守约，终鲜差失。里闬姻党，情谊无涯。富贵轮流，转眼虚花。出入以度，惟公惟平。夜半叩门，尔心不惊。永言孝思，世德作求。我语谆谆，我心悠悠。毫釐不差，神明临汝。良心不昧，三复斯语。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"52f093e11b6c7580ac6ae86c79448400","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6441866,"Sentence":"诗咏多福，易言馀庆。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shī yǒng duō fú ，yì yán yú qìng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441867,"Sentence":"积善之家，罔不繁盛。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jī shàn zhī gū ，wǎng bú fán chéng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441868,"Sentence":"眇予小子，厕名士绅。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"miǎo yú xiǎo zi ，cè mǐng shì shēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441869,"Sentence":"愧无实德，裨补君民。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"kuì mó shǐ dé ，bì bǔ jūn mǐn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441870,"Sentence":"未能治国，愿教吾家。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wèi néng zhì guó ，yuàn jiāo wú gū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441871,"Sentence":"敷诚布衷，寂听无哗。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fū chéng bù zhōng ，jì tīng mó huā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441872,"Sentence":"凡我宗人，无忽予言。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fán wǒ zōng rén ，mó hū yú yán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441873,"Sentence":"洗心涤虑，培根达源。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xi xīn dǐ lǜ ，péi gēn dá yuán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6441874,"Sentence":"敬奉天地，孝养双亲。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jìng fèng tiān 地，xiào yǎng shuāng qīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"Englis